{"tid":2118969,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球暖化致海冰融化 北極熊80年內恐絕種","createTime":"2020-07-21T23:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T00:35:26.000Z","uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cafec7421cfc2bc8134629ff7cfbd91f86c06edb","tid":2118969,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T23:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/st/95187f47430f763cea01d51fc738aee0/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200721/_2020072122390349136.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F680p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fst%2F95187f47430f763cea01d51fc738aee0%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200721%2F_2020072122390349136.jpg&h=59558a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據「自然氣候變遷」（Nature Climate Change）期刊今天刊登的研究，氣候變遷正造成北極熊覓食困難、飢餓致死，預料80年內可能幾乎消失。<br />\n<br />\n科學家在期刊文章指出，部分地區的北極熊早就陷入惡性循環，海冰面積縮小，使得北極熊獵捕海豹時間縮短。科學家還說，北極熊體重下降，削弱牠們在沒有食物的情況下，度過北極寒冬的機會。<br />\n<br />\n國際北極熊中心（Polar Bears International）首席科學家安斯特拉普（Steven Amstrup）說：「在冰層結冰且能回去覓食前，北極熊面臨更長的斷食期。」安斯特拉普在電郵中表示：「如果很神奇地，就算氣溫上升，海冰面積還能維持不變，北極熊可能就安然無恙。但問題是牠們的棲息地實際上正在融化。」<br />\n<br />\n研究得出的結論是，在當前趨勢下，分析北極熊的13個子群體，其中有12個將在80年之內，因北極地區飛速變化而數量劇減。北極地區暖化速度是整個地球的兩倍。安斯特拉普說，在2100年之前，氣候變遷將嚴重影響北極熊延續後代，甚至可能除了加拿大伊麗莎白女王群島（Queen Elizabeth Islands）的子群體之外亦難以產下幼熊。<br />\n<br />\n此設想是預期地球表面均溫會升到比工業化之前的基準高攝氏3.3度的情況。但即使人類能把全球升溫控制在2.4度以內，恐怕也只能讓北極熊多存續一段時間。北極熊面臨的威脅並非氣溫上升本身，而是這個位於食物鏈頂端的掠食者無法適應快速變化的環境。"},{"pid":"c7a748703a8bc0929a81edfe38aaed468a2ec42c","tid":2118969,"uid":123765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:01:40.000Z","msg":"應該絕種既係人類"},{"pid":"c59d00a5311c04a33a87adebd2bd90a732c5a30c","tid":2118969,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:09:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbbe275fc9b7a4a1603fa1b74c5c291d9d6e93de","tid":2118969,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/3hI5Mj_1KtnMBOTdtm_c6I83KfU7VJHI-ylBbqhlifmXxwGSeu8WgFQZ5z2vJFahlwcfedPsXEao8zvTrfolV2D9Fsvgf0rnEu1O6rK0_c3w-KJxIh7wFA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F3hI5Mj_1KtnMBOTdtm_c6I83KfU7VJHI-ylBbqhlifmXxwGSeu8WgFQZ5z2vJFahlwcfedPsXEao8zvTrfolV2D9Fsvgf0rnEu1O6rK0_c3w-KJxIh7wFA&h=f8b5f994&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d374c0c84d2b6815ea28850cf3bc199edb2755f","tid":2118969,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a748703a8bc0929a81edfe38aaed468a2ec42c","tid":2118969,"uid":123765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:01:40.000Z","msg":"應該絕種既係人類"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:10:31.000Z","msg":"地球可以無人類<br />\n人類唔可以無地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804036d4400a9bb0a4c2a44e74dc1d9893b8dcba","tid":2118969,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:12:36.000Z","msg":"適者生存"},{"pid":"86eac0151eedb6bfad4cf251d6b358a1a9ce4d7a","tid":2118969,"uid":40932,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:21:15.000Z","msg":"人都未生存到，成日講北極熊海龜"},{"pid":"5863ad31cd8e756053e3e1319ae17a627cbd0573","tid":2118969,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:35:26.000Z","msg":"同支人講北極熊熊膽好補壯陽保肺，今年都可以實施絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}